snippet: Algeria and Cameroon began with away wins in the final round of African Cup qualifiers. Algeria, Africa’s top-ranked team, beat Ethiopia, 2-1, to start the decisive competition for Morocco 2015 with 3 points.

headline.main: Algeria and Cameroon Win African Cup Qualifiers
